sortAndCountVoList.enDescription: Capacitors are devices that store electricity and play an important role in tuning, bypassing, coupling, filtering and other circuits. JLCPCB offers types of capacitor assemblies from industry-leading manufacturers such as Murata Electronics, TDK, AVX, Kemet and more.

Circuit protection devices are used to protect electrical circuits from damage caused by hazards. JLCPCB has a wide variety of Circuit Protection for Assembly, including Vishay Intertech, Littelfuse, and Texas Instruments.

The connector is a device that connects two active devices and transmits current or signals. 
JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality Connectors for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers such as TE Connectivity, Molex, Amphenol ICC, Samtec and more.

Development boards & tools are programmable boards containing various electronic components and interfaces for controlling, communicating, and processing data. They are commonly used in electronic manufacturing, automation control, industrial control, and other fields.JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality Development Boards & Tools for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers such as Arduino, Raspberry Pi, STMicroelectronics, NXP Semiconductors and more.

A diode is an electronic component.JLPCB has different types of Diodes for PCB Assembly, which are from international manufacturers, such as Vishay Intertech, NXP Semicon, Microchip Tech, and STMicroelectronics.

Electronic Tools/Instruments/Consumables are used to create signals and capture responses from electronic devices under test. JLCPCB has a wide variety of equipment tools used for Assembly.  They are from the international brand AVAGO, Bosch Sensortec Prokit's Industries.

Electrical controls can be on/off controls, time rate controls, current rate controls, and position rate controls. JLCPCB has different types of Embedded Processors & Controllers for PCB assembly from Exas Instruments, Microchip Tech, NXP Semicon and Infineon Technologies.

Passive Components and Discrete Semiconductors can be used as filters for avoiding many interference from outside signals.JLCPCB Assembly part library has different types of Filters from international manufacturers, such as Littelfuse, STMicroelectronics, Vishay Intertech, Maxim Integrated, and Analog Devices.

Components, integrated circuits, or semiconductors that are in stock with various distributors and manufacturers.
JLCPCB has great manufacturers and high availability of the electronic components necessary to perform PCB assembly services.

The communications module encodes the message onto the network's physical medium representing a link to another system. JLCPCB has a wide variety of modern sensors, integrated circuits with WiFi and Bluetooth included, energy-saving devices, actuators, relays, and mechanical/electrical drive systems to communicate an electronic card with the cloud or the internet.JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality IoT/Communication Modules for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers such as SIMCom, Quectel, Telit, Sierra Wireless and more.

Memory provides users with convenient, secure, and sufficiently large storage space. It is widely used in the manufacturing, construction, electrical, industrial, and electronic equipment fields. Memory from international brands Maxim Integrated, Texas Instruments, and Microchip Tech are available at JLCPCB for assembly.

Optocoupler&LED& Infrared is a semiconductor device that transfers an electrical signal between isolated circuits using light. Optoelectronics is available at JLCPCB Assembly Parts Library from industry-leading manufacturers including Everlight Elec, Infineon Technologies, Littelfuse and Vishay Intertech.

Optoelectronics is the application of electronic devices that source, detect and control light. Optoelectronics is available at JLCPCB Assembly parts library from industry-leading manufacturers including Everlight Elec, Infineon Technologies, Littelfuse, and Vishay Intertech.

childSortList.sortName: Voltage Regulators - Linear, Low Drop Out (LDO) Regulators

sortAndCountVoList.enDescription: Power management ICs are used to manage power devices in host systems and are commonly used in cell phones, various mobile terminal devices, and in the mechatronic field.JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality Power Management ICs for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers such as Texas Instruments, Analog Devices, STMicroelectronics, ON Semiconductor and more.

A relay is a piece of electrical equipment that sends television, radio, and satellite signals from one place to another.JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality Relays for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers such as Omron, Panasonic, TE Connectivity, Fujitsu and more.

The resistor is one of the essential components in any electronic circuit, and JLCPCB has the Resistor from industry-leading manufacturers such as Vishay Intertech, TE Connectivity, Maxim Integrated, and Analog Devices to be used in the PCB assembly service.

Sensors are detection devices that can meet the requirements of transmission, processing, storage, display, recording and control of information. JLCPCB has a wide variety of sensors for application in the commercial, medical, and aeronautical industries, and industry.
JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality Sensors for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers such as Bosch Sensortec, STMicroelectronics, Analog Devices, Infineon Technologies and more.

A switch is a device in a computer network that connects other devices. JLCPCB Assembly parts library has different types of switches from the best manufacturers such as Connectivity, Mitsumi Electric, BOURNS, and Omron Electronics.

A Triode/MOS Tube/Transistor is a semiconductor device that controls the current in electronic products. Which can be used in a wide range of applications such as amplifiers, switches, or sensors. JLCPCB offers a wide range of high-quality Triode/MOS Tube/Transistor devices for PCB assembly from industry-leading manufacturers including Infineon Technologies, Vishay Intertech, Nexperia, Texas Instruments and more.
